    • 构造器概要

      构造器 
      构造器和说明
      BlockSheetedFrame(gregtech.api.unification.material.Material[] materials)
      Modified Material, Harvest Tool and Sound Type by Block#getMaterial(), Block#getHarvestTool() and Block#getSoundType() because we should declare Gregtech material, when it is wooden material, then return axe and wood sound type, otherwise return wrench and metal sound type.

      • getBlockFaceShape

        public net.minecraft.block.state.BlockFaceShape getBlockFaceShape(net.minecraft.world.IBlockAccess worldIn,
                                                                  net.minecraft.block.state.IBlockState blockState,
                                                                  net.minecraft.util.math.BlockPos blockPos,
                                                                  net.minecraft.util.EnumFacing face)
        从类复制的说明: net.minecraft.block.Block
        Get the geometry of the queried face at the given position and state. This is used to decide whether things like buttons are allowed to be placed on the face, or how glass panes connect to the face, among other things.

        Common values are SOLID, which is the default, and UNDEFINED, which represents something that does not fit the other descriptions and will generally cause other things not to connect to the face.

        覆盖:
        getBlockFaceShape 在类中 net.minecraft.block.Block
        返回:
        an approximation of the form of the given face
